monq.jfa.actions

Class Unmatched

  • java.lang.Object
    • monq.jfa.actions.Unmatched

  • public class Unmatched
extends java.lang.Object

    contains actions to switch the default behaviour of a DfaRun object.

    The static FaAction objects supplied here do not allow to change their priority. If it is really necessary to have such an object with a different priority than zero, wrap it into a Run object and call AbstractFaAction.setPriority(int) for it.

    Author:
    © 2004 Harald Kirsch
